Package: bizdays
Title: Functions to handle business days calculations
Description: bizdays is a small set of functions to help with calculations
    which make use of business days. It works based on a list of holidays
    which is passed as an argument. Its interface is simple and flexible
    operating on vector of dates.
    bizdays can be fairly used for fixed income calculations.
    Many countries make intense use of business days to price
    financial instruments, like bonds and derivatives.
